file.name: api_key_blocked_openAPI.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.5
  title: API key Blocked API
servers:
  - url: http://mockBackend:2383/v2
paths:
  '/pet/{petId}':
    get:
      summary: Find pet by ID
      parameters:
        - name: petId
          in: path
          description: ID of pet to return
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int64
      responses:
        '200':
          description: successful operation
        '404':
          description: Pet not found
      security:
        - APIKeyAuth: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    APIKeyAuth:
      type: apiKey
      name: x-api-key
      in: header
